---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import AssetGarden from '../../components/lab/AssetGarden.vue';
---

<Layout title="數位資產花園 | TaiCalc Lab" description="將你的資產配置可視化為一座花園。現金是水，股票是樹，債務是害蟲。">
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-[#fafaf9]">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
      <!-- Nav -->
      <nav class="flex mb-8" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <ol class="inline-flex items-center space-x-1 md:space-x-3">
          <li class="inline-flex items-center">
            <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center text-sm font-medium text-stone-500 hover:text-emerald-600">首頁</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <span class="mx-2 text-stone-400">/</span>
              <a href="/lab" class="text-sm font-medium text-stone-500 hover:text-emerald-600">實驗室</a>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li aria-current="page">
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <span class="mx-2 text-stone-400">/</span>
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-emerald-600">資產花園</span>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </nav>

      <AssetGarden client:load />

      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-20 text-center text-stone-500 text-sm">
        <p>你的花園長什麼樣子？這反映了你的財務內心世界。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
